metadata.name: Salisby Dalisby’s Happy Lighted Worlds #1/12
metadata.description: Salisby Dalisby’s happy lighted plates and giant rocks with vast cavern worlds. All non element structures that are 100 percent free of pollution, no toxins, zero radiation sources and zero radioactive lighted rock at all depths at all locations. All lighted rock materials have zero dust, no poop decay, no decaying vegetation.  There are no seed plants nor seed trees present.  There are Googalim lighted mists present at times when needed.
